      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from one of his companions, from Ibrahim Bin Abu Al Balaad, from Ali Bin Al Mugheira, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘From the misery of the life is the evil ride’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "10. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from Muhammad ibn ‘Isa from certain persons of his people from Ibrahim ibn abu al-Balad from Ali ibn al-Mughirah who has said the following: “Abu Ja‘far, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘It is a misfortune in life to have a bad stumper.’” "
        ]
      }
